We have sixteen aircraft still in the park -- nine of them helicopters.\~ I read in the morning paper where they are calling it a strange kind of contest, modern against primitive.\~ I don't see it that way at all.\~
 I don't see how he could be walking those trails unseen with all the people we have searching.
